            "**request_id**: Unique request",
            "**eTag**: The ETag of the entity",
            "**enabled**: Allows to forcefully disable emails on app or user level",
            "**settings**: The settings the user has for the app",
            "**userId**: The unique id (UUID) of the user",
            "**appId**: Application ID",
            "**user_enabled**: A flag indicating if settings are enabled at user/global level"
          ]
        },
        {
          "$lang": "json",
          "$code": {
